53
00:07:39.877 --> 00:07:42.504
Hold off on draining the pool
until we can test it. okay?

54
00:07:42.588 --> 00:07:45.299
- Yeah. right.
- And y'all stay in town.

55
00:07:45.966 --> 00:07:47.676
Y'all have any guns in the house?

56
00:07:47.759 --> 00:07:48.886
Why are you asking us?

57
00:07:48.969 --> 00:07:50.804
I'm sorry. but I... I have to ask--

58
00:07:50.888 --> 00:07:52.806
Why don't you go downtown
and question him?

59
00:07:53.724 --> 00:07:55.350
If y'all had kept
an eye on him like I said.

60
00:07:55.434 --> 00:07:57.227
maybe my friend would be alive right now.

61
