Yeah. it's Georgia. I got guns.

65
00:08:08.071 --> 00:08:09.615
Y'all got a nine millimeter?

66
00:08:09.698 --> 00:08:10.908
Yeah.

67
00:08:10.991 --> 00:08:12.784
I'm sorry to ask.
but do you mind if I see it?

68
00:08:12.868 --> 00:08:14.786
- Hang on.
- Would you be willing to head down

69
00:08:14.870 --> 00:08:17.831
- to the station and make that statement?
- No. absolutely. we definitely will.

70
00:08:17.915 --> 00:08:19.124
Yes. and any other de--

71
